data.description: SELLER IS RELATED TO SELLING AGENT!!!!! Easy to show! Fully update 2,524sq ft home! Generous size master bedroom suite with newly custom walk-in closet an master bathroom (just renovated in 2021) 3 additional large bedrooms and main bath on second level.  Spacious living room, formal dining room (freshly painted), cozy family room with fireplace spacious eat in kitchen, half bath and laundry room on main level, screened in sunroom and huge fenced in backyard.  full finished basement and 2 car attached garage.  new roof 2020, new gutters 2020, new windows and well covers to basement 2021, new sliding door in kitchen leading to sunroom, new stainless steel fridge and microwave (2021).  Dual furnace (recently serviced), and two sump pumps.  Easy aces sto shopping and restaurants.  Close to elementary school and easy access to I-57.  Close to the bus line and to metra, must I say anymore.  THE PLAYGROUND DOES NOT STAY!!!!!This home has all the bell and whistles you would ever dream of:  Please schedule your showing today before it's gone.
